text: "Late to da Party (F*CK BET)" is a song by American rappers Lil Nas X and YoungBoy Never Broke Again. Both Nas and Young boy wrote the song's lyrics with Take A Daytrip and Cheese. This song is a diss track towards Black Entertainment Television, because of BET's homophobic remarks, as the song's cover is a man urinating on a BET award placed in the toilet. ==References== Category:2022 songs Category:Lil Nas X songs
title: Late to da Party
